 approach to the cell formation problem with alternative process plans," International Journal of Advanced Manufacturing Technology, Vol. 24, pp. 834-840 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.418). Yeh, J.Y., and T.H. Wu, 2005, “Solutions for Product Configuration Management—An Empirical Study,” Artificial Intelligence for Engineering Design, Analysis and Manufacturing, Vol. 19, No. 1, pp. 39-47. Yeh, J.Y., J. C. Fu, C.C. Wu, Z. B. Lu, and J. W. Chai, 2005, “Myocardial Border Detection by Branch-and-Bound Dynamic Programming in Magnetic Resonance Images,” Computer Methods and Programs in Biomedicine, Vol. 79, No. 1, pp. 19-29 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.604). Yeh, J.Y. and J.C. Fu, 2005, “Double Simulated Annealing for Functional MRI Analysis,” Journal of Chinese Institute of Industrial Engineering, Vol. 22, No. 6, pp. 497-508, 2006 JCIIE best paper award (EI, TSSCI). Fu, J.C., S.K. Lee, S.T.C. Wong, J.Y. Yeh, A.H. Wang, and H.K. Wu, 2005, “Image Segmentation Feature Selection and Pattern Classification for Mammographic Microcalcifications,” Computerized Medical Imaging and Graphics, Vol. 29, pp. 419-429 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.909). Tai-Hsi Wu, J.Y. Yeh, and C.C. Chang, 2005, “Solving generalized assignment problem using Lagrangian relaxation,” Journal of Quality, Vol. 12, No. 4, pp. 313-322. 葉進儀、吳泰熙、張維昌，2006，「結合平行基因演算法與排列啟發式方法解二維長方形排列問題」，品質學報，第13捲第1期，頁59-70。 Yeh, J.Y., Tai-Hsi Wu, and J.M. Chang, 2007, “Parallel genetic algorithms for product configuration management on PC cluster systems," International Journal of Advanced Manufacturing Technology, Vol. 31, No. 11-12 , pp. 1233-1242 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.418). Yeh, J.Y. and W.S. Lin, 2007, “Using simulation technique and genetic algorithm to improve the quality care of a hospital emergency department,” Expert Systems with Applications, Vol. 32, No. 4, pp. 1073-1083 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.957). Yeh, J.Y. and J.C. Fu, 2007, “Parallel adaptive simulated annealing for computer-aided measurement in functional MRI analysis,” Expert Systems with Applications, Vol. 33, No. 3, pp. 706-715 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.957). 葉進儀、林彣珊、朱慶餘，2007，「應用平行基因演算法解護理人員排班問題」，品質學報，第14捲第3期，頁337-350。 Yeh, J. Y. and J.C. Fu, 2008, “A Hierarchical Genetic Algorithm for Segmentation of Multi-Spectral Human-Brain MRI,” Expert Systems with Applications, Vol. 35, No. 2 (SCI, Impact Factor: 0.957).  


